<text><body>
<lb n="0211b17"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0211b18"/>
<lb n="0211b19"/><head type="no">No. 1087 [No. 1086]</head>
<lb n="0211b20"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0211008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>觀自在如意輪菩薩瑜伽法<note n="0211009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要＋（出大部）細註【明】</note><app n="0211009"><lem>要</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">要<note place="inline">出大部</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0211b21"/><note n="0211010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】</note><note n="0211010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0211010"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0211b22"/>
<lb n="0211b23"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0211011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】</note><note n="0211011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0211011"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>唐南天竺國三<note n="0211012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藏＋（法師）【三】</note><note n="0211012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0211012"><lem>藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">藏法師</rdg></app>金剛智譯</byline>
<lb n="0211b24"/><div1 type="jing"><lg><l>我今順瑜伽</l><l>金剛頂經說</l>
<lb n="0211b25"/><l>摩尼蓮花部</l><l>如意念誦法</l>
<lb n="0211b26"/><l>修此三昧故</l><l>能如觀自在</l>
<lb n="0211b27"/><l>先擇其弟子</l><l>族姓敬法者</l>
<lb n="0211b28"/><l>多人所敬愛</l><l>智慧而勇進</l>
<lb n="0211b29"/><l>決定毘離耶</l><l>覺慧常不捨</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0211c" n="0211c"/>
<lb n="0211c01"/><l>盡孝於父母</l><l>淨信於三寶</l>
<lb n="0211c02"/><l>樂修菩薩行</l><l>於四無量心</l>
<lb n="0211c03"/><l>剎那無有間</l><l>常樂大乘法</l>
<lb n="0211c04"/><l>住於菩薩戒</l><l>恭敬阿闍梨</l>
<lb n="0211c05"/><l>一切諸聖者</l><l>成就堅固力</l>
<lb n="0211c06"/><l>丈夫之勇猛</l><l>善通相應門</l>
<lb n="0211c07"/><l>常樂寂靜行</l><l>智慧無所畏</l>
<lb n="0211c08"/><l>以戒常嚴身</l><l>精修祕密乘</l>
<lb n="0211c09"/><l>敬依理趣道</l><l>一心無所&CB00385;</l>
<lb n="0211c10"/><l>常樂聞妙法</l><l>曾入三昧耶</l>
<lb n="0211c11"/><l>從師獲灌頂</l><l>既蒙印可已</l>
<lb n="0211c12"/><l>不久當成就</l><l>弟子具此相</l>
<lb n="0211c13"/><l>方可為傳授</l><l>此即如意寶</l>
<lb n="0211c14"/><l>能成諸事業</l><l>如經說處所</l>
<lb n="0211c15"/><l>山間及流水</l><l>清淨阿蘭若</l>
<lb n="0211c16"/><l>隨樂之&CB00589;谷</l><l>離諸危怖難</l>
<lb n="0211c17"/><l>隨力嚴供具</l><l>行人面於西</l>
<lb n="0211c18"/><l>漫提自在王</l><l>次禮餘方佛</l>
<lb n="0211c19"/><l>以五輪著地</l><l>如教之敬禮</l>
<lb n="0211c20"/><l>雙膝長跪已</l><l>合掌虛心住</l>
<lb n="0211c21"/><l>誠心盡陳說</l><l>三業一切罪</l>
<lb n="0211c22"/><l>我從過去世</l><l>流轉於生死</l>
<lb n="0211c23"/><l>今對大聖尊</l><l>盡心而懺悔</l>
<lb n="0211c24"/><l>如先佛所懺</l><l>我今亦如是</l>
<lb n="0211c25"/><l>願垂加持力</l><l>眾<note n="0211013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝罪【三】</note><note n="0211013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝罪【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0211013"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">罪</rdg></app>悉清淨</l>
<lb n="0211c26"/><l>以此大<note n="0211014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">願＝敬【宋】</note><app n="0211014"><lem>願</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">敬</rdg></app>故</l><l>自他獲無垢</l></lg>
<lb n="0211c27"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0211c28"/><p type="dharani">唵　莎&CB00085;皤&CB00085;輸馱　薩婆達麼　莎&CB00085;皤
<lb n="0211c29"/>&CB00085;輸度&CB00776;</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0212a" n="0212a"/>
<lb n="0212a01"/><p>行者次應隨喜一切諸佛菩薩所集福智</p>
<lb n="0212a02"/><lg><l>過現三世佛</l><l>菩薩及眾聖</l>
<lb n="0212a03"/><l>所集諸善根</l><l>合掌盡隨喜</l>
<lb n="0212a04"/><l>如我身所集</l><l>歡喜無有異</l></lg>
<lb n="0212a05"/><p>次應右膝著地芙蓉合掌置於頂上<note n="0212001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">想＝頂【三】</note><note n="0212001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想＝頂【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0212001"><lem>想</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">頂</rdg></app>禮一
<lb n="0212a06"/>切如來及菩薩足。密言曰</p>
<lb n="0212a07"/><p type="dharani">唵　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><note n="0212002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline">二合</note>微<note place="inline">微<note n="0212003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吉＝害【明】</note><app n="0212003"><lem>吉</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">害</rdg></app>反</note></p>
<lb n="0212a08"/><p>禮諸佛已全加半加或輪王加隨意而坐</p>
<lb n="0212a09"/><lg><l>作此坐印已</l><l>觀遍虛空佛</l>
<lb n="0212a10"/><l>已身各於前</l><l>住彼眾聖會</l>
<lb n="0212a11"/><l>止觀從膝上</l><l>旋舞當心合</l>
<lb n="0212a12"/><l>如蓮之未敷</l><l>想禮於諸佛</l>
<lb n="0212a13"/><l>次結三昧印</l><l>當心堅固縛</l>
<lb n="0212a14"/><l>檀慧禪智<note n="0212004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00594;＝堅【宋】</note><app n="0212004"><lem>&CB00594;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">堅</rdg></app></l><l>金剛蓮花印</l>
<lb n="0212a15"/><l>通持蓮花者</l><l>警覺眾聖已</l>
<lb n="0212a16"/><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0212a17"/><p type="dharani">唵　跋日囉<note n="0212005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0212005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二合〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline">二合</note>三<note n="0212006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝麼【三】</note><note n="0212006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">磨＝麼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0212006"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>耶
<lb n="0212a18"/>薩怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0212a19"/><lg><l><note n="0212007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝猶【三】＊</note><note n="0212007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＝猶【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0212007"><lem>由</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">猶</rdg></app>結此印故</l><l>佛及善逝子</l>
<lb n="0212a20"/><l>諸大名稱者</l><l>妙觀察攝受</l>
<lb n="0212a21"/><l>憶昔本誓願</l><l>對於遍照尊</l>
<lb n="0212a22"/><l>不違教令故</l><l>加持使圓滿</l></lg>
<lb n="0212a23"/><p>次結一切諸佛如來安樂悅意歡喜三昧耶印</p>
<lb n="0212a24"/><lg><l>十度堅固縛</l><l>忍願中交合</l>
<lb n="0212a25"/><l>檀慧與禪智</l><l>各相合而&CB00594;</l></lg>
<lb n="0212a26"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0212a27"/><p type="dharani">唵　三麼耶　呼<note place="inline"><note n="0212008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】</note><note n="0212008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去＋（聲）【明】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0212008"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>蘇<note place="inline"><note n="0212009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0212009"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>囉哆　薩怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0212a28"/><lg><l><app type="＊" source="0212007"><lem>由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">猶</rdg></app>示此印故</l><l>諸佛及菩薩</l>
<lb n="0212a29"/><l>一切執金剛</l><l>皆悉妙歡喜</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0212b" n="0212b"/>
<lb n="0212b01"/><l>次當開心戶</l><l>入金剛智字</l>
<lb n="0212b02"/><l>觀於二乳上</l><l>右怛囉左吒</l>
<lb n="0212b03"/><l>如宮室戶扇</l><l>殊勝金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0212b04"/><l>三業同時發</l><l>拍心開兩字</l></lg>
<lb n="0212b05"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0212b06"/><p type="dharani">唵　跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱怛&CB02744;<note place="inline">二合</note>吒</p>
<lb n="0212b07"/><lg><l>無始熏種子</l><l>所集之塵勞</l>
<lb n="0212b08"/><l>今以召罪印</l><l>集之欲摧碎</l>
<lb n="0212b09"/><l>十度堅固縛</l><l>忍願申如針</l>
<lb n="0212b10"/><l>進力屈如鉤</l><l>心想召諸罪</l>
<lb n="0212b11"/><l>想彼眾罪狀</l><l>植髮裸黑形</l>
<lb n="0212b12"/><l>反印刺於心</l><l>觸已誦密語</l>
<lb n="0212b13"/><l>三業相應故</l><l>能召諸罪積</l>
<lb n="0212b14"/><l>誦此召集已</l><l>方作摧碎法</l></lg>
<lb n="0212b15"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0212b16"/><p type="dharani">唵　薩婆播波迦哩灑拏　尾輸馱娜　三磨
<lb n="0212b17"/>耶　跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>　吽若</p>
<lb n="0212b18"/><lg><l>召入於掌已</l><l><note n="0212010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">施＝方【三】</note><note n="0212010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施＝方【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0212010"><lem>施</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">方</rdg></app>作摧<note n="0212011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">破＝碎【三】</note><note n="0212011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">破＝碎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0212011"><lem>破</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">碎</rdg></app>法</l>
<lb n="0212b19"/><l>前印內相叉</l><l>稱&CB00805;縛諸罪</l>
<lb n="0212b20"/><l>忍願俱申直</l><l>有怛&CB02744;吒字</l>
<lb n="0212b21"/><l>想為金剛杵</l><l>相拍如摧山</l>
<lb n="0212b22"/><l>忿句及怒形</l><l>能淨諸惡趣</l>
<lb n="0212b23"/><l>誦已忍願拍</l><l>七三隨所宜</l></lg>
<lb n="0212b24"/><p type="dharani">唵　跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>播尼<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>尾莎怖吒也　薩
<lb n="0212b25"/>跢播耶滿馱娜&CB00135;&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>母訖灑<note place="inline">二合</note>也薩婆
<lb n="0212b26"/>播也孽底<note n="0212012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔丁以反〕－【明】</note><app n="0212012"><lem><note place="inline">丁以反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>毘藥<note place="inline">二合重呼</note>薩婆薩怛蔓<note n="0212013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無繁＝無【元】，〔無繁反〕－【明】</note><note n="0212013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔無繁反〕－【明】，無繁＝無【元】</note><app n="0212013"><lem><note place="inline">無繁反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">無反</note></rdg></app><note n="0212014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（凡）＋薩【元】【明】</note><app n="0212014"><lem>薩</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">凡薩</rdg></app>
<lb n="0212b27"/>婆怛他孽多跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>三磨耶吽　怛囉
<lb n="0212b28"/><app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>吒</p>
<lb n="0212b29"/><lg><l>以此相應門</l><l>先佛方便故</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0212c" n="0212c"/>
<lb n="0212c01"/><l>三業所積罪</l><l>無量極重障</l>
<lb n="0212c02"/><l>作此摧滅已</l><l>如火焚枯草</l>
<lb n="0212c03"/><l>有情常愚迷</l><l>不知此理趣</l>
<lb n="0212c04"/><l>如來大悲故</l><l>開此祕<note n="0212015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妙＝密【三】</note><note n="0212015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙＝密【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0212015"><lem>妙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>門</l>
<lb n="0212c05"/><l>次當結入印</l><l>內如來智字</l>
<lb n="0212c06"/><l>二羽堅固縛</l><l>禪智入於中</l>
<lb n="0212c07"/><l>以進力二度</l><l>相拄如環勢</l>
<lb n="0212c08"/><l>觀前八葉蓮</l><l>其上置阿字</l>
<lb n="0212c09"/><l>二點嚴飾故</l><l>妙字方名惡</l>
<lb n="0212c10"/><l>色白如珂雪</l><l>流散千光明</l>
<lb n="0212c11"/><l>想以進力支</l><l>捻字安心內</l>
<lb n="0212c12"/><l>三業齊運用</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0212c13"/><p type="dharani">唵　跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>廢<note place="inline">亡計反</note>捨惡</p>
<lb n="0212c14"/><lg><l>既想入心中</l><l>字相逾光耀</l>
<lb n="0212c15"/><l>此即法界體</l></lg>
<lb n="0212c16"/><lg><l>行者應是觀</l><l>不久悟寂靜</l>
<lb n="0212c17"/><l>法本不生故</l><l>三世諸如來</l>
<lb n="0212c18"/><l>金剛身口意</l><l>皆以妙方便</l>
<lb n="0212c19"/><l>持在金剛拳</l><l>以此闔心門</l>
<lb n="0212c20"/><l>智字獲堅固</l><l>便屈進力度</l>
<lb n="0212c21"/><l>拄於禪智背</l><l>以印觸胸已</l>
<lb n="0212c22"/><l>即誦此妙言</l></lg>
<lb n="0212c23"/><p type="dharani">唵　跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>母瑟致&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0212c24"/><lg><l>行者住等引</l><l>二羽堅固縛</l>
<lb n="0212c25"/><l>仰置於臍下</l><l>禪智蓮<note n="0212016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">葉＝華【三】</note><note n="0212016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">葉＝華【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0212016"><lem>葉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">華</rdg></app>形</l>
<lb n="0212c26"/><l>此名三昧印</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0212c27"/><p type="dharani">唵　三<note n="0212017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼地＝磨他【三】</note><note n="0212017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼地＝磨他【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0212017"><lem>麼地</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">磨他</rdg></app>　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>迷<note place="inline">二合</note>紇哩<note place="inline">引二合</note></p>
<lb n="0212c28"/><lg><l>出息及入息</l><l>住阿那波那</l>
<lb n="0212c29"/><l>想佛遍虛空</l><l>彈指警覺我</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0213a" n="0213a"/>
<lb n="0213a01"/><l>佛子汝云何</l><l>成無上等覺</l>
<lb n="0213a02"/><l>不知諸如來</l><l>實相之妙法</l>
<lb n="0213a03"/><l>既聞警覺已</l><l>行者復白言</l>
<lb n="0213a04"/><l>云何名真實</l><l>願最勝尊說</l>
<lb n="0213a05"/><l>諸佛皆歡喜</l><l>作如是勝言</l>
<lb n="0213a06"/><l>善哉摩訶薩</l><l>能作如是問</l>
<lb n="0213a07"/><l>汝想於心中</l><l>所內惡字門</l>
<lb n="0213a08"/><l>以字徹於心</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0213a09"/><p type="dharani">唵　止多&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">丁以反</note>味能<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212008"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>迦路弭</p>
<lb n="0213a10"/><lg><l>當默誦一遍</l><l>便想為月輪</l>
<lb n="0213a11"/><l>倍欲精進故</l><l>復誦妙言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0213a12"/><p type="dharani">唵　母提止多　母怛跛<note place="inline">二合</note>娜夜弭</p>
<lb n="0213a13"/><lg><l>能令心月輪</l><l>圓滿甚清淨</l>
<lb n="0213a14"/><l>中想妙蓮花</l><l>上安寶金剛</l></lg>
<lb n="0213a15"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0213a16"/><p type="dharani">唵　底瑟奼　麼尼<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>跋日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼
<lb n="0213a17"/><note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0213a18"/><lg><l>引量同虛空</l><l>周遍於三界</l>
<lb n="0213a19"/><l>復誦此妙言</l><l>金剛語離聲</l></lg>
<lb n="0213a20"/><p type="dharani">唵　薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉麼尼<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0213a21"/>麼<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0213a22"/><lg><l>於此引妙蓮</l><l>流放千光焰</l>
<lb n="0213a23"/><l>一一光明中</l><l>無量佛剎土</l>
<lb n="0213a24"/><l>剎中有妙蓮</l><l>想持寶蓮者</l>
<lb n="0213a25"/><l>持寶蓮勝幢</l><l>幢中出妙聲</l>
<lb n="0213a26"/><l>誰有薄福者</l><l>當滿一切願</l>
<lb n="0213a27"/><l>住是寂三昧</l><l>為利諸有情</l>
<lb n="0213a28"/><l>如是菩薩類</l><l>皆住於等引</l>
<lb n="0213a29"/><l>從蓮花胎藏</l><l>妙放千光明</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0213b" n="0213b"/>
<lb n="0213b01"/><l>皆為利眾生</l><l>檀波羅密等</l>
<lb n="0213b02"/><l>遍入諸三昧</l><l>理趣善巧門</l>
<lb n="0213b03"/><l>為<note n="0213001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00517;＝愍【三】</note><note n="0213001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00517;＝愍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0213001"><lem>&CB00517;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">愍</rdg></app>念有情</l><l>作無量方便</l>
<lb n="0213b04"/><l>化身為種種</l><l>從生及涅槃</l>
<lb n="0213b05"/><l>轉大妙法輪</l><l>皆從意寶出</l>
<lb n="0213b06"/><l>所說之妙法</l><l>皆以<note n="0213002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輪＝轉【三】＊</note><note n="0213002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輪＝轉【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0213002"><lem>輪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">轉</rdg></app>成就</l>
<lb n="0213b07"/><l>以<app type="＊" source="0213002"><lem>輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">轉</rdg></app>為妙智</l><l>能斷諸結使</l>
<lb n="0213b08"/><l>猶轉大法輪</l><l>此為福智路</l>
<lb n="0213b09"/><l>次皆正觀察</l><l>漸斂其智蓮</l></lg>
<lb n="0213b10"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0213b11"/><p type="dharani">唵僧<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212008"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>訶囉麼抳<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0213b12"/><note n="0213003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔麼〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0213003"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0213b13"/><lg><l>所在諸如來</l><l>皆入為一體</l>
<lb n="0213b14"/><l>猶如於明鏡</l><l>能現於萬像</l>
<lb n="0213b15"/><l>法界自性體</l><l>住於金剛蓮</l>
<lb n="0213b16"/><l>即變其寶蓮</l><l>為真多菩薩</l>
<lb n="0213b17"/><l>手持如意寶</l><l>六臂身金色</l>
<lb n="0213b18"/><l>皆想於自身</l><l>頂髻寶莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0213b19"/><l>冠坐自在王</l><l>住於說法相</l>
<lb n="0213b20"/><l>第一手思惟</l><l>愍念有情故</l>
<lb n="0213b21"/><l>第二持意寶</l><l>能滿一切願</l>
<lb n="0213b22"/><l>第三持念珠</l><l>為度傍生苦</l>
<lb n="0213b23"/><l>左按光明山</l><l>成就無傾動</l>
<lb n="0213b24"/><l>第二持蓮手</l><l>能淨諸非法</l>
<lb n="0213b25"/><l>第三手持輪</l><l>能轉無上法</l>
<lb n="0213b26"/><l>六臂廣博體</l><l>能遊於六道</l>
<lb n="0213b27"/><l>以大悲方便</l><l>斷諸有情苦</l>
<lb n="0213b28"/><l>行者如是觀</l><l>坐於月輪中</l>
<lb n="0213b29"/><l>身流千光明</l><l>項背皆圓光</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0213c" n="0213c"/>
<lb n="0213c01"/><l>復想心月輪</l><l>亦有寶蓮花</l>
<lb n="0213c02"/><l>以是能堅固</l><l>無動觀己身</l>
<lb n="0213c03"/><l>為離諸妄想</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0213c04"/><p type="dharani">唵暱里<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0213004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【宋】【元】</note><app n="0213004"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg></app><note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212009"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>底瑟奼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>囉怛那　跋
<lb n="0213c05"/>日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline">引<anchor id="fxT20p0213c05"/>二合</note><note n="0213005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怛＝&M010527;【明】</note><app n="0213005"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&M010527;</rdg></app>麼<note place="inline">二合</note>句&CB00776;
<lb n="0213c06"/>三<note n="0213006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＝摩【三】</note><note n="0213006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼＝摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0213006"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>喻&CB00776;<note n="0213007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【三】</note><note n="0213007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＝麼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0213007"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>訶三麼喻&CB00776;薩婆怛多<note n="0213008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘗＝&CB03870;【三】</note><note n="0213008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘗＝&CB03870;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0213008"><lem>蘗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB03870;</rdg></app>多
<lb n="0213c07"/>避三菩地囉怛那跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0213c08"/>怛麼<note place="inline">二合</note>句&CB00776;</p>
<lb n="0213c09"/><lg><l>以此法加持</l><l>十度芙蓉合</l>
<lb n="0213c10"/><l>進力屈如寶</l><l>印心額喉頂</l>
<lb n="0213c11"/><l>吽字想於心</l><l>怛囉安於額</l>
<lb n="0213c12"/><l>紇哩當喉上</l><l>惡字置於頂</l>
<lb n="0213c13"/><l>猶此布想故</l><l>此身如金剛</l>
<lb n="0213c14"/><l>復誦此密言</l><l>蓮花語為聲</l></lg>
<lb n="0213c15"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0213009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＋（囉）【元】【明】</note><app n="0213009"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">囉囉</rdg></app>　怛娜　跋日囉<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>達麼　紇哩<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二
<lb n="0213c16"/>合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0213c17"/><lg><l>次應結灌頂</l><l>智者合蓮掌</l>
<lb n="0213c18"/><l>進力如寶形</l><l>檀惠開相近</l>
<lb n="0213c19"/><l>置額誦密言</l><l>心想佛<note n="0213010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">灌＝囉【三】</note><note n="0213010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">灌＝囉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0213010"><lem>灌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>頂</l></lg>
