<lb n="0214c01"/><p type="dharani">唵　只惹<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>娜&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>倪<note place="inline">魚&CB00242;<app type="＊" source="0214008"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>帝吽</p>
<lb n="0214c02"/><lg><l>次應結舞印</l><l>前印左右旋</l>
<lb n="0214c03"/><l>合芙蓉妙掌</l><l>安於頂上散</l>
<lb n="0214c04"/><l>由此四供養</l><l>能獲大神通</l></lg>
<lb n="0214c05"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0214c06"/><p type="dharani">唵　只惹<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>娜　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00135;&CB00069;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0214c07"/>帝吽</p>
<lb n="0214c08"/><lg><l>作此四供養</l><l>能成最勝事</l>
<lb n="0214c09"/><l>次結外供養</l><l>喜心而獻之</l>
<lb n="0214c10"/><l>運心無邊界</l><l>蓮花焚香法</l>
<lb n="0214c11"/><l>諸佛誠言說</l><l>為利諸有情</l>
<lb n="0214c12"/><l>蓮掌向下散</l><l>猶如焚香勢</l>
<lb n="0214c13"/><l>誦此祕密言</l><l>想供養香雲</l>
<lb n="0214c14"/><l>周遍虛空界</l><l>供養諸聖眾</l></lg>
<lb n="0214c15"/><p type="dharani">唵　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>只惹娜　度閉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0214003"><lem>平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">平聲</rdg></app></note>噁</p>
<lb n="0214c16"/><lg><l>次應結花印</l><l>以三十二相</l>
<lb n="0214c17"/><l>莊嚴諸如來</l><l>觀妙色花雲</l>
<lb n="0214c18"/><l>運心遍一切</l><l>如前合蓮掌</l>
<lb n="0214c19"/><l>上散如花勢</l><l>供養諸如來</l>
<lb n="0214c20"/><l>及諸善逝子</l><l>想滿虛空界</l>
<lb n="0214c21"/><l>花雲妙芬馥</l><l>劫樹極端嚴</l>
<lb n="0214c22"/><l>誦此祕<note n="0214016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妙＝密【明】</note><app n="0214016"><lem>妙</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>言</l><l>三業齊運用</l></lg>
<lb n="0214c23"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>只惹娜　補&CB00612;閉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0214003"><lem>平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">平聲</rdg></app></note>吽</p>
<lb n="0214c24"/><lg><l>眾生無明覆</l><l>離於智慧光</l>
<lb n="0214c25"/><l>為彼淨除故</l><l>應結智燈印</l>
<lb n="0214c26"/><l>以前蓮花掌</l><l>禪智&CB00594;相逼</l>
<lb n="0214c27"/><l>心想摩尼燈</l><l>遍照虛空界</l>
<lb n="0214c28"/><l>無量光所出</l><l>誦此密言曰</l></lg>
<lb n="0214c29"/><p type="dharani">唵　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>只惹　那&CB00135;閉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0214003"><lem>平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">平聲</rdg></app></note></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0215a" n="0215a"/>
<lb n="0215a01"/><lg><l>智者次應結</l><l>解脫塗香印</l>
<lb n="0215a02"/><l>為淨眾生故</l><l>獻此尸羅香</l>
<lb n="0215a03"/><l>二手散蓮掌</l><l>當心塗香勢</l>
<lb n="0215a04"/><l>十度成熏習</l><l>香海遍虛空</l>
<lb n="0215a05"/><l>獻佛及所尊</l><l>誦此祕密語</l></lg>
<lb n="0215a06"/><p type="dharani">唵　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>只惹娜巘提吽</p>
<lb n="0215a07"/><lg><l>內外供養已</l><l>然後應順念</l>
<lb n="0215a08"/><l>結祕根本印</l><l>以對密言主</l>
<lb n="0215a09"/><l>先誦根本言</l><l>分明七遍已</l>
<lb n="0215a10"/><l>平掌當於心</l><l>忍願如蓮葉</l>
<lb n="0215a11"/><l>進力摩尼狀</l><l>餘度盡如幢</l>
<lb n="0215a12"/><l>誦根本密言</l><l>思滿有情願</l></lg>
<lb n="0215a13"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0215a14"/><p type="dharani">娜麼<note n="0215001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【宋】</note><app n="0215001"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>怛娜　怛羅夜也　娜莫阿唎耶
<lb n="0215a15"/>　&CB00085;魯枳帝　濕&CB00085;囉耶　菩地薩怛&CB00085;耶
<lb n="0215a16"/>　<note n="0215002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【宋】</note><app n="0215002"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>訶薩怛&CB00085;耶　摩訶迦嚕抳迦耶　怛姪
<lb n="0215a17"/>他唵　斫迦羅靺<note place="inline">彈舌</note>低震跢麼抳　摩訶&CB00425;
<lb n="0215a18"/>頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>迷嚕嚕底瑟吒入&CB00085;&CB00256;　阿迦哩　灑
<lb n="0215a19"/>耶吽泮吒　薩&CB00085;<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p>
<lb n="0215a20"/><lg><l>次結心祕密</l><l>依前根本印</l>
<lb n="0215a21"/><l>戒方檀惠縛</l><l>名為本心印</l>
<lb n="0215a22"/><l>一切諸意願</l><l>應心之所念</l>
<lb n="0215a23"/><l>由結此印故</l><l>皆悉得成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0215a24"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0215a25"/><p type="dharani">唵　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>迷震哆麼抳　入&CB00085;&CB00256;吽</p>
<lb n="0215a26"/><lg><l>次結隨心印</l><l>二手堅固<note n="0215003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝&CB00085;【三】</note><note n="0215003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛＝&CB00085;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0215003"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0215a27"/><l>進力摩尼形</l><l>禪智並而申</l>
<lb n="0215a28"/><l>戒方亦舒直</l><l>檀惠相交&CB00594;</l>
<lb n="0215a29"/><l>誦此心中心</l></lg>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0215b" n="0215b"/>
<lb n="0215b01"/><p type="dharani">唵　&CB00085;囉娜　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>迷吽</p>
<lb n="0215b02"/><lg><l>次想尊口中</l><l>流出祕密言</l>
<lb n="0215b03"/><l>分明成字道</l><l>五色光照耀</l>
<lb n="0215b04"/><l>間錯殊勝色</l><l>入於諭岐口</l>
<lb n="0215b05"/><l>列心月輪中</l><l>瑩如紅頗<note n="0215004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">犁＝梨【三】</note><note n="0215004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">犁＝梨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0215004"><lem>犁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">梨</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0215b06"/><l>一一諦思惟</l><l>順理隨覺悟</l>
<lb n="0215b07"/><l>住定而修習</l><l>入於阿字門</l>
<lb n="0215b08"/><l>即入輪字觀</l><l>皆遍觀諸字</l>
<lb n="0215b09"/><l>此名三昧念</l><l>獲智及解脫</l>
<lb n="0215b10"/><l>由此相應故</l><l>不久成種智</l>
<lb n="0215b11"/><l>若當聲順念</l><l>最勝妙奇特</l>
<lb n="0215b12"/><l>住於本尊觀</l><l>不應急躁心</l>
<lb n="0215b13"/><l>不高亦不下</l><l>不緩亦不急</l>
<lb n="0215b14"/><l>智者離分別</l><l>及諸妄想心</l>
<lb n="0215b15"/><l>若誦洛叉遍</l><l>所求皆悉地</l>
<lb n="0215b16"/><l>二手持念珠</l><l>頗知與蓮子</l>
<lb n="0215b17"/><l>螺珠及餘寶</l><l>無瑕光好者</l>
<lb n="0215b18"/><l>當穿一百八</l><l>一一誦七遍</l>
<lb n="0215b19"/><note n="0215005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心及…鬘已〕二十字－【三】</note><note n="0215005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔心及…鬘已〕二十字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0215005" word-count="20"><lem><l>心及心中心</l><l>及毘俱多羅</l>
<lb n="0215b20"/><l>作此法加持</l><l>穿貫珠鬘已</l></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0215b21"/><l>當心一一度</l><l>與莎訶齊聲</l>
<lb n="0215b22"/><l>一千與<note n="0215006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">百八＝八百【三】</note><note n="0215006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">百八＝八百【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0215006"><lem>百八</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">八百</rdg></app></l><l>隨力而念誦</l>
<lb n="0215b23"/><l>四時或三時</l><l>此法後夜勝</l>
<lb n="0215b24"/><l>如意輪經中</l><l>本教佛所說</l>
<lb n="0215b25"/><l>若如是修習</l><l>現世證初地</l>
<lb n="0215b26"/><l>過此十六生</l><l>成無上菩提</l>
<lb n="0215b27"/><l>何況世悉地</l><l>現生不如意</l>
<lb n="0215b28"/><l>隨力念誦已</l><l>重結三昧印</l>
<lb n="0215b29"/><l>復為八供養</l><l>發遣密言主</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1087.0215c" n="0215c"/>
<lb n="0215c01"/><l>二羽堅固縛</l><l>忍願蓮葉形</l>
<lb n="0215c02"/><l>從心至面散</l><l>頂上合花掌</l>
<lb n="0215c03"/><l>想尊虛空中</l><l>復道還本宮</l></lg>
<lb n="0215c04"/><p>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0215c05"/><p type="dharani">唵　&CB00425;頭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0212002"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲</rdg></app></note>麼<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>薩怛&CB00085;<app type="＊" source="0212005"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>紇哩穆</p>
<lb n="0215c06"/><lg><l>發遣聖者已</l><l>自住本尊觀</l>
<lb n="0215c07"/><l>或於閑靜處</l><l>轉讀摩訶衍</l>
<lb n="0215c08"/><l>楞伽與花嚴</l><l>般若及理趣</l>
<lb n="0215c09"/><l>如是等經教</l><l>思惟而修習</l>
<lb n="0215c10"/><l><note n="0215007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦讀＝讀誦【三】</note><note n="0215007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦讀＝讀誦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0215007"><lem>誦讀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">讀誦</rdg></app>經典已</l><l>自恣行住坐</l>
<lb n="0215c11"/><l>乃至於寢息</l><l>不<note n="0215008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">間＝問【元】</note><app n="0215008"><lem>間</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">問</rdg></app>菩提心</l>
<lb n="0215c12"/><l>不久當悉地</l><l>金剛藏所說</l>
<lb n="0215c13"/><l>此大悲軌儀</l><l>不擇日及宿</l>
<lb n="0215c14"/><l>時食與澡浴</l><l>若淨與不淨</l>
<lb n="0215c15"/><l>常應不間斷</l><l>遠離於散亂</l>
<lb n="0215c16"/><l>不營諸世務</l><l>念畢發誓願</l>
<lb n="0215c17"/><l>結三昧耶印</l><l>禮佛菩薩已</l>
<lb n="0215c18"/><l>隨意而經行</l><note n="0215009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔由是…結集〕四十字－【三】</note><note n="0215009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔由是…結集〕四十字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0215009" word-count="40"><lem><l>由是積福業</l>
<lb n="0215c19"/><l>解脫本願力</l><l>能令諸有情</l>
<lb n="0215c20"/><l>速獲一切智</l><l>此上四句願</l>
<lb n="0215c21"/><l>金剛儀軌述</l><l>為利眾生故</l>
<lb n="0215c22"/><l>我今同結集</l></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lg>
<lb n="0215c23"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>觀自在<note n="0215010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如意輪菩薩＝菩薩如意輪【宋】</note><app n="0215010"><lem>如意輪菩薩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">菩薩如意輪</rdg></app>瑜伽法要</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>